  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The acoustic radiation force impulse (ARFI) technology provides real-time measurements of
      tissue stiffness.

      Aim: Using the ARFI ultrasonography, the investigators aims are to complete the correlation
      and validity studies between visceral ARFI quantification and the referenced Metavir fibrosis
      scoring and to conduct subsequent innovative studies on liver diseases.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Using ARFI technology, we are establishing a complete hepatic and visceral shear wave
      spectrum to correspond to the entire METAVIR fibrosis scoring and various functional
      stratifications.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
